data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the charming community of Holly by the Sea, Navarre. This exquisite residence boasts 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and over 2500 square feet of meticulously designed living space, all situated on a generous .46-acre lot. As you approach the home, you are greeted by a spacious porch, inviting you to step inside and explore further. The open floor plan provides a seamless flow throughout, with thoughtfully chosen light colors enhancing the sense of space and tranquility. A stunning focal wall surrounds the wood-burning fireplace, adding warmth and character to the living area. The kitchen, featuring a breakfast bar, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Recent upgrades include a new hot water heater, HVAC system blower, and upgraded smoke alarms for added peace of mind. The home also boasts granite countertops throughout and includes new washer and dryer units for added convenience. Step outside, and you'll discover a meticulously landscaped yard, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. A covered porch area provides a shaded retreat, while a walkway leads to a charming gazebo area, ideal for enjoying the serene surroundings. The fully fenced yard offers privacy and security, making it ideal for both family gatherings and quiet moments of solitude. Additionally, the home comes equipped with a new solar portable generator with a panel, ensuring energy efficiency and reliability. With warranty coverage paid through March 2028, you can enjoy worry-free living in this stunning Navarre residence. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own and experience the epitome of coastal living in Holly by the Sea. Located just 12 minutes to Navarre Beach, just 32 minutes to Downtown Pensacola. Book your Private showing now !!! A few HOA Amenities to mention are the indoor and outdoor pools, workout room, childcare are just a few to mention.
